{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0001","text":"也許這個理由不便形容你未夠膽講","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌焦慮","愛情觀","自我懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["理由","形容","膽講"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,5,4,5,0,3,2,0,0,5,2,4,9,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jaa5","heoi2","ze5","go3","lei5","jau4","bat1","bin6","jing4","jung4","nei5","mei6","gau3","daam2","gong2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"這個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"理由","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不便","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"形容","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"未夠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"膽","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"此句使用『也許』開頭，表達不確定與猜測的語氣，並以『不便形容』、『不夠膽講』暗示對方不願明言的原因與說話者的不安。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0002","text":"也許不愛我只因藐視我未能似藝人好看","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌焦慮","愛情觀","自我懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不愛","藐視","藝人","好看"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,3,4,5,9,3,5,2,5,2,0,5,2,0,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jaa5","heoi2","bat1","oi3","ngo5","zi2","jan1","miu5","si6","ngo5","mei6","nang4","ci5","ngai6","jan4","hou2","hon3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"因","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"藐視","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"未能","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"似","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"藝人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"好看","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"延續上一句的猜測，直接點出『不愛我』的可能性，並將原因歸結於『藐視』和外貌不如『藝人』，語氣顯得自卑。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
