{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0004","text":"而你竟疏遠全沒有情講","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌焦慮","愛情觀","關係疏遠"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["疏遠","情講"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,9,3,5,0,2,5,0,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ji4","nei5","ging2","so1","jyun5","cyun4","mut6","jau5","cing4","gong2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"而","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"竟","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"疏遠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"全","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"情講","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『而』連接上句的發現，『竟疏遠』帶有驚訝與無奈，『全沒有情講』直接點出關係的冷淡與隔閡。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0005","text":"假使我漂亮 性格縱使不喫香 如明星賣相","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌焦慮","自我肯定","理想化"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["漂亮","性格","喫香","明星","賣相"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,5,3,2,4,4,4,9,3,4,3,0,0,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["gaa2","si2","ngo5","piu1","loeng6","sing3","gaak3","zung3","si2","bat1","hek3","hoeng1","jyu4","ming4","sing1","maai6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"假使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"漂亮","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"性格","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"縱使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"喫香","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"明星","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"賣相","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『假使』提出假設情境，『漂亮』與『性格不喫香』形成對比，『如明星賣相』進一步強調外貌的重要性。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
