{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0007","text":"多幾個對象 怕你愛得比我傷 有另一下場","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["外貌焦慮","關係擔憂","潛在威脅"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["對象","怕","愛得比我傷","一下場"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,4,4,2,4,5,4,3,9,5,3,5,2,3,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["do1","gei2","go3","deoi3","zoeng6","paa3","nei5","oi3","dak1","bei2","ngo5","soeng1","jau5","ling6","jat1","haa6","coeng4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"多","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"幾個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"對象","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"比","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"傷","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"另","pos":"DET"},{"text":"一下場","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『多幾個對象』暗示競爭者出現，『怕你愛得比我傷』表達了對關係不穩定的恐懼，『有另一下場』預示了可能的悲劇結局。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0008","text":"但愛情沒價 何必幻想","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情觀","價值觀","現實思考"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["愛情","沒價","幻想"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,0,2,4,0,3,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","oi3","cing4","mut6","gaa3","ho4","bit1","waan6","soeng2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"愛情","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"沒價","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"何必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"幻想","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"『但』轉折，『愛情沒價』、『何必幻想』表達了對愛情價值的質疑和對不切實際幻想的否定。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0009","text":"值錢的不是善良","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情觀","價值觀","現實思考"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["值錢","善良"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,0,3,3,2,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik6","cin4","dik1","bat1","si6","sin6","loeng4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"值錢","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"不是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"善良","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『值錢的不是善良』直接點出，在愛情中，善良似乎不是最重要的價值，暗示了外貌或其它因素更受重視。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0010","text":"殘忍到 怕去承認真相","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情觀","價值觀","殘酷現實"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["殘忍","真相"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,4,4,4,0,2,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["caan4","jan2","dou3","paa3","heoi3","sing4","jing6","zan1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"殘忍","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"去","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"承認","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"真相","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『殘忍到』加強語氣，『怕去承認真相』表達了對殘酷現實的恐懼與逃避，情感非常負面。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0011","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0011","text":"你的工作不開心便在乎我贈你的湯","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["關係維繫","付出與關懷","價值判斷"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["工作","開心","在乎","湯"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,3,4,3,3,3,2,2,0,5,2,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","dik1","gung1","zok3","bat1","hoi1","sam1","bin6","zoi6","fu4","ngo5","zang6","nei5","dik1","tong1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"工作","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"開心","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"便","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在乎","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我贈","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"湯","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『你的工作不開心』描述對方的情緒，『便在乎我贈你的湯』則強調說話者透過實際行動（送湯）來表達關心，以此作為關係的衡量標準。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0012","text":"到我親吻你即使要面對面時你沒有在乎一看","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["關係維繫","付出與關懷","被忽略"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["親吻","面對面","沒有在乎","一看"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,3,5,5,3,9,4,2,4,2,0,5,2,5,2,0,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dou3","ngo5","can1","man5","nei5","zik1","si2","jiu3","min6","deoi3","min6","si4","nei5","mut6","jau5","zoi6","fu4","jat1","hon3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"親吻","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"面對面","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"時","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"在乎","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一看","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"『到我親吻你』描述親密行為，『即使要面對面時你沒有在乎一看』則表達了即使在親密時刻，對方也未給予關注，語氣顯得失落與被忽略。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0013","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0013","text":"原諒我 誤解可給你踏實地幸福一趟","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["關係維繫","付出與關懷","誤解與原諒"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["原諒","誤解","踏實","幸福"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,2,9,9,3,5,2,2,2,2,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyun4","loeng6","ngo5","ng6","gaai2","ho2","kap1","nei5","daap6","sat6","dei6","hang6","fuk1","jat1","tong3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"原諒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"誤解","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"給","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"踏實","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"幸福","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一趟","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"『原諒我』再次出現，『誤解可給你踏實地幸福一趟』表達了說話者希望透過自己的方式（即使是誤解）給予對方幸福，帶有自我辯護的意味。"},"source":{"title":"假使我漂亮","artists":["關心妍"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1056","prev_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_5YWz5b-D5aaN_MTA1Ng_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
